hopobject.body: Through friends pioglitazone goodrx Diversifying Taiwan’s export markets and thereby avoiding overdependence on mainland China has long been a goal of this Ministry. One focus of current policy is to expand exports to emerging markets. Thus, for example, Taiwan’s exports to the ten member states of Association of Southeast Asian Nations as a ratio of our total exports have steadily increased to 19.2% for the first five months of 2013, from 18.8% in 2012, 16.7% in 2011, and 15.3% in 2010.
